{"tid":2457991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲Jennie扮性感女神 被彈濃妝顯老態","createTime":"2021-03-23T05:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T14:54:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f2d419e871871bd5d8541873edd5973dc90cbd","tid":2457991,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WoqiA49y61WvEHsGafMjXocucvM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5NNBMSZFHRGTTPGJ4WMB3AFBWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWoqiA49y61WvEHsGafMjXocucvM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5NNBMSZFHRGTTPGJ4WMB3AFBWQ.jpg&h=0cc45fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國天團BIGBANG隊長G-DRAGON（GD），上月被爆暗撻同門女團BLACK PINK的25歲成員Jennie一年，兩人所屬的YG事務所沒有直接否認戀情。爆出戀情後Jennie依舊專注工作，今日凌晨她就於IG公開多張拍攝時的花絮照，不過就遭網民批評她顯老態。<br />\n<br />\n模仿招牌造型<br />\n於公開的新相及影片中，見到Jennie穿上露肩連身裙，化上濃妝示人，似是模仿已故性感女神瑪麗蓮夢露（Marilyn Monroe）的招牌造型，Jennie亦用英文留言：「感覺自己成為了電影演員。」不過照片公開後，有網民就指Jennie望落不似25歲，認為她的樣子「顯老」、「皮膚狀態不佳」等，未知是否跟其妝容抑或她當時太疲倦有關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_z3s6qvS0mH7nFC8Q0QD0SfAz_I=/802x934/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5GKGQXAUBBDALIZIORP6XTEJUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_z3s6qvS0mH7nFC8Q0QD0SfAz_I%3D%2F802x934%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5GKGQXAUBBDALIZIORP6XTEJUA.jpg&h=5312787b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xxtuDxPuF-kdB1zyb6SptoEl3WI=/802x1060/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BUJIKYA4CFBBTOV3JCUN37YT7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxxt